txt.en: 'I can't recall a time when things were so dire in Staddle.'
'I wonder if the folk out Buckland way have such troubles as these....'
'Will we need to leave Staddle and resettle in a far away land?'
'This whole business is mighty queer, if you ask me.'
'No good will come of this, believe you, me!'
'I reckon we'll all starve, come wintertime.'
'I was going to make a pie, but now I haven't got any rhubarb!'
